title: Collection-Alonzo T. Jones(Babylon to New Jerusalem,Greater Purp
description:
This is an amazing collection of booklets by Alonzo Trevier Jones which deal with the principle of Church organization in the light of Christ our Righteousness and unveil a perspective which very few understand.

Contained are:

From Babylon to New Jerusalem
The Greater Purpose
This is The Church
Some History, Experience and Facts
An Appeal for Evangelical Christianity

Also contains David Clayton's book A Time to Choose which talks about the mark of the beast and the satanic forces behind it.
